<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1396708-i-ve-read-two-other-books-by-jodi">I&#39;ve read two other books by Jodi Picoult&#39;s and loved them both. Her way of dealing with timely issues is nothing but awe inspiring to another author who wishes to do the same. Her characters are believable and the plots unfold in a way that leaves one wondering and wanting more at every turn of the page. How many found A Spark of Light to be another of JP&#39;s wonderful reads?</a>
</div>
