<div class='spoiler'>
This answer contains spoilers…
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    I think Picoult planned this as a surprise twist to be revealed towards the end. But right from the beginning I always assumed that she was the shoote<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    I think Picoult planned this as a surprise twist to be revealed towards the end. But right from the beginning I always assumed that she was the shooter's daughter - I thought in some big twist she would turn out to be someone else's daughter... This line was quite meh for me<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
